<% provide(:title, "Get in Touch") %>
<h1>Get in Touch</h1>
<p class="large">Thank you so much for reaching out to me! Because I’m still attending college I can’t make any promises, but I will do my best to respond as soon as possible. I look forward to getting back to you!</p>
<p class="large">“The Lord, He is my strength and my song, and He has become my salvation. He is <em>my God</em>.”<br/>
(Exodus 15:2)</p>
<br/>
<h2>Website under construction</h2>
<h3>Please contact me through LinkedIn or Facebook until form is working</h3>
<br/>
<%= form_with class: 'contact-form' do |f| %>
<%= f.text_field :name, placeholder: 'Name', class: 'field' %>
<br/>
<%= f.email_field :email, placeholder: 'Email', class: 'field' %>
<br/>
<%= f.text_area :message, placeholder: 'Message', class: 'field field-message' %>
<br/>
<%= f.submit 'Send Message', class: 'button field submit-button' %>
<% end %>